      "title": "Temporary grassland composed of grass",
      "category": "temporary_grassland_composition",
      "active_at_start": true,
      "description": "Land on which the vegetation is dominated by grass such as perennial ryegrass or sheep's fescue."
    },
    {
      "id": "C.9.2",
